casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Riley Andrew SPITLER, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158249
COA: 331962 Supreme Court of Michigan. January 23, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the June 28, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
